<title>USA: MAPICS Inc separates from parent company.</title>
<headline>MAPICS Inc separates from parent company.</headline>
<dateline>ATLANTA 1997-08-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>MAPICS, until recently a business unit of Marcam Corp, has announced that it has separated from its parent company and will conduct business as MAPICS Inc.</p>
<p>MAPICS' enterprise resource planning solutions are targeted at mid-sized global manufacturers, typically companies with revenues between $20 million and $500 million or divisions of Fortune 1000 companies.</p>
